to view Port numbers open serverindex.xml file in below path.

/opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/Dmgr/config/cells/Dmgrcell/nodes/Dmgrnode/serverindex.xml


to do Fedaration follow the steps.
1. go to Appserver profile or custom profile location and go to bin.
2. run the following command.
./addNode.sh <DMGR host name> <SOAP connector port number>



After fedaration goto admin console.
1. under System Adminstration goto nodeAgent stop the node agent
2. in terminal goto profile bin directory run ./startNode.sh



